movie.title: United 93
movie.plot: A real time account of the events on United Flight 93, one of the planes hijacked on 9/11 that crashed near Shanksville, Pennsylvania when passengers foiled the terrorist plot.
movie.awards: Nominated for 2 Oscars. Another 29 wins & 55 nominations.
